<Class name="CM_TempReading" id="4cefe339-1bda-4c26-91fb-5a7e8442216f">
    <superclass name="CM_Object"/>
    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>

This is a total shambles which will be sorted out in 7.
All these classes have different ways of storing temperatures 
and trackeditem reference. There are methods to try and
have a common interface to all these.
This all caught up the following 
CM_TrackedItem fields
.packTempDetails
.logTemperatures.
CM_DailyReeferTempByDateDict

RS 17 October 2002.</text>
